                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7385" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">DMD-0016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6629 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">知之愈明，则行之愈笃： 国有检测机构能否依靠决策逆风翻盘？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The clearer you know, the more certain you will be：Can state-owned detection institution turn the tide by making decisions?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">罗裕梅, 张语珂,王敏瑞, 王晓彤, 赵荣浩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">昆明高海拔电器检测有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电器检测；国有企业；决策分析；效用理论；社会学习理论；制度逻辑</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Electrical Detection; State-owned Enterprise; Decision-making Analysis; Utility Theory; Social Learning Theory; Institutional Logic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着检验检测行业规则政策的逐渐完善，优质民营检验检测机构迅速发展，国有企业A电器检测公司为应对行业竞争大环境，提出了“站稳脚跟谋发展”的战略目标。本案例主要叙述A电器检测公司几位总经理及相应部门解决决策困境的过程：首先，通过公司高层会议讨论，明确了“拓展新业务，提高业务量”是实现公司战略目标的根本，而“设引进新设备”则是其中的关键；其次，在宋先生和郑先生的讨论过程中，通过数据信息的分析和梳理，确定了设备采购决策问题的方法和建模思路；最后，根据公司实际情况提出相关问题，引导学生自发思考并利用效用理论解释风险对决策的影响机制，以及借助制度逻辑、社会学习理论对决策者风险偏好变化现象进行分析，进一步提升学生经管实践与经典理论间的衔接度。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the improvement regulation and policies in inspection and detection industry, high-quality private institutions which work for inspection and detection have developed rapidly. In order to cope with the competitive pressure, A Electrical Detection Company, a state-owned enterprise, has put forward the strategic goal of “keep footing and seek development”. This case mainly describes the process of several general managers and corresponding departments of A Electrical Detection Company to solve the decision-making dilemma. Firstly, through the discussion of senior management meeting, it is clear that “expanding new businesses and increasing their quantity” is the root to achieve company&#39;s strategic goal, while &quot;introducing new equipment&quot; is the key point. Secondly, during the discussion between Mr. Song and Mr. Zheng, through the analysis and sorting of data information, the methods and modeling ideas of equipment procurement decision-making were determined. Finally, relevant questions are put forward according to the actual situation of the company. In this way, students are guided to think spontaneously and use utility theory to explain the influence mechanism of risk on decision making, as well as analyze the influencing factors of the change of the style of decision makers with the help of institutional logic and social learning theory to further improve the degree of connection between students&#39; economic management practice and classical theories.
Keywords: Electrical Detection; State-owned Enterprise; Decision-making Analysis; Utility Theory; Social Learning Theory; Institutional Logic
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《数据模型与决策》、《运筹学》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策树；敏度分析；效用理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-07</td>
                            </tr>
